ivardefs.name: family
ivardefs.desc: The part of a name that links to the genealogy. In some cultures (e.g. Eritrea) the family name of a son is the first name of his father.

ivardefs.name: period
ivardefs.desc: Indicates the period of time when this name was valid for the named person.

ivardefs.name: prefix_
ivardefs.desc: Part of the name that is acquired as a title due to academic, legal, employment or nobility status, etc. and that appears at the start of the name.

ivardefs.name: suffix_
ivardefs.desc: Part of the name that is acquired as a title due to academic, legal, employment or nobility status, etc. and that appears at the end of the name.

ivardefs.name: text
ivardefs.desc: A full text representation of the name.

ivardefs.name: use
ivardefs.desc: Identifies the purpose for this name.
